  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>‼ WARNING</strong>: MAY CAUSE SEIZURES FOR INDIVIDUALS PHOTOSENSITIVE EPILEPSY <strong>‼</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>DEATHTRIP</strong></i> is a web-comic movement shooter extravaganza set in a mystical dreamscape. The world is unpredictable and you die fast. All weapons and mechanics are intentionally overtuned. May cause anger, nausea and vomiting. Do not play this game if you have any of the following conditions:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heart issues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anger issues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Photosensitive epilepsy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Schizophrenia</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fainting goat syndrome</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Parkinson's disease (or any other neurodegenerative disease (this game makes it worse))</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is medical advice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909010/extras/fe62181c9bf547721113cada3e841f37.poster.avif?t=1762328783\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909010/extras/fe62181c9bf547721113cada3e841f37.webm?t=1762328783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909010/extras/fe62181c9bf547721113cada3e841f37.mp4?t=1762328783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*Developer note: DEATHTRIP is an ongoing project and is constantly being updated with new stages, weapons and content. Everything is subject to change and high-score strategies are always evolving. </i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>‼ WARNING</strong>: MAY CAUSE SEIZURES FOR INDIVIDUALS PHOTOSENSITIVE EPILEPSY <strong>‼</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>DEATHTRIP</strong></i> is a web-comic movement shooter extravaganza set in a mystical dreamscape. The world is unpredictable and you die fast. All weapons and mechanics are intentionally overtuned. May cause anger, nausea and vomiting. Do not play this game if you have any of the following conditions:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heart issues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anger issues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Photosensitive epilepsy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Schizophrenia</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fainting goat syndrome</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Parkinson's disease (or any other neurodegenerative disease (this game makes it worse))</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is medical advice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909010/extras/fe62181c9bf547721113cada3e841f37.poster.avif?t=1762328783\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909010/extras/fe62181c9bf547721113cada3e841f37.webm?t=1762328783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909010/extras/fe62181c9bf547721113cada3e841f37.mp4?t=1762328783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*Developer note: DEATHTRIP is an ongoing project and is constantly being updated with new stages, weapons and content. Everything is subject to change and high-score strategies are always evolving. </i></p>",
